text: Cea cng xya khid penxankhad wa brrda phu thi piti yin tx sing thi phwk khea kratha læa chxb thi ca di rab ka ra chmchey nı sing thi phwk khea midi kratha nan (ca rxdphn kar lngthosʹ pi di) dangnan cea cng xya khid penxankhad wa phwk khea ca mi thang rxdphn cak kar lngthosʹ pi di læa sahrab phwk khea nan khux kar lngthosʹ xan cebsæb
